  "text": "(35) The second Donders' surface was reported in [CITATION_1] , where the surface parameters are obtained from actual measurements of a set of human heads. Only one sample surface S2 has been used in this paper and is described as The cost function described on SO(3) has the form Fig. 7 shows that for small ε, trajectory follows the constraint quickly even when the initial condition is away from the constraint. Initial and final condition on λ is chosen to be zero. Fig. 10 shows that under the S2 constraint, trajectory follows the constraint quickly, though not as quickly as in Fig. 7 .",
